    "(OpenAI 2018)",
    "In developing ChatGPT, OpenAI made use of public domain and fair-use text corpora to train ChatGPT.",
    "The largest, CommonCrawl, contains petabytes of data scraped from web pages, news articles and copyrighted books (O'Sullivan and Dickerson 2020).",
    "It is to my knowledge the largest publicly-available data repository.",
    "According to their FAQ section, \"Common Crawl is […] dedicated to providing a copy of the Internet […] at no cost for the purpose of research and analysis\" (CommonCrawl 2023)."
